WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:08.747
We did it, family. We stopped him—the man I told you I saw in the spirit who was going to try to do something at Trump's rally.

00:00:08.748 --> 00:00:25.675
There were two different articles sent to me by two different viewers telling me, "Hey Brandon, look what happened at Coachella."I told everybody we must pray for Coachella because there's an attempt on Trump that was going to be there, and I told everybody, "Hey, they're going to try to shoot people in the crowd.

00:00:25.676 --> 00:00:37.155
This is going to be a big deal; we have to pray against this."Well, nothing was said all day yesterday about any kind of anything in the news.

00:00:37.156 --> 00:00:54.399
Well, today I'm getting all these articles from people telling me, "Brandon, look, he was stopped."He had a fake security pass, a fake press pass; he had all kinds of things to try to get inside the event to try to get close to Trump.

00:00:54.400 --> 00:01:07.553
So I just want to give all the glory to God, for He shows the watchman on the wall to warn them to pray on behalf of whatever He needs them to be praying for.

00:01:07.554 --> 00:01:13.998
We are making a difference, and I just want to encourage you all.

00:01:13.999 --> 00:01:18.740
Thank you for coming and praying with me and my little prayer group here.

00:01:18.741 --> 00:01:24.306
I am so excited, I'm speechless. I'm just like, "Wow, thank you, Lord.

00:01:24.307 --> 00:01:28.834
Look at what we're doing."We're making a difference, and I just want to encourage you to keep going.

00:01:28.835 --> 00:01:33.938
We have to pray; there are still things we have to pray about clear up until after the election.

00:01:33.939 --> 00:01:41.146
So we're going to be making these prayer videos. Here's our prayer video today. So God bless you all and thank you.

00:01:41.147 --> 00:01:47.830
And then they had the big prayer thing in Washington, D.C., and nothing happened there. We interceded for that.

00:01:47.831 --> 00:01:55.635
I was praying for protection over the people, that no secret enemy attacks or anything would happen during the big prayer thing with Jonathan Cahn.

00:01:55.636 --> 00:02:04.251
From what I saw, nothing evil happened at all there, and there were probably 20,000 to 30,000 people there.

00:02:04.252 --> 00:02:12.354
It was a lot of people in the camera shot who were interceding, taking communion, and praying for this nation, and they were worshiping Jesus.

00:02:12.355 --> 00:02:19.758
You could feel the presence of the Lord tangibly when I was watching it. If you didn't watch that, go back and watch that again.

00:02:19.759 --> 00:02:24.694
I believe they probably have a replay on Jonathan Cahn's YouTube channel.

00:02:24.695 --> 00:02:30.320
So I encourage everybody to watch that; that was a real blessing. It blessed me; I could feel the presence of the Lord.

00:02:30.321 --> 00:02:42.253
It made me want to weep because people were crying out for repentance, seeking the Lord, and this is what it's going to take for revival.

00:02:42.254 --> 00:03:01.508
If my people, who are called by my name, will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways, He said we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.

00:03:01.509 --> 00:03:09.711
I believe that God is not done with America yet, that there is one last revival that will take place.

00:03:09.712 --> 00:03:17.351
He said, "Brandon, there will be a shaking to awaken,"and whatever it takes, His remnant right now is preparing themselves.

00:03:17.352 --> 00:03:25.636
We're ready, and we're getting our hearts ready before Him right now as the glorious church ready for a great revival.

00:03:25.637 --> 00:03:36.605
I believe with all my heart we're about to see the demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God like we've never seen before.

00:03:36.606 --> 00:03:59.751
Like He said to me, "Brandon, the old wells are becoming uncapped, and we're going to go down to the deep parts."People say, "Well, we want to go back and just see those old revivals."No, I want something new, something fresh—a new, fresh experience of the presence of the Lord, not the old thing.

00:03:59.752 --> 00:04:07.318
Let's do something new. So I'm excited for what the Lord is about to do.

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:37.858
The old revivals, the old Harbinger Church, the old tent revivals, the old outpouring like it was at Azusa—I believe that we'll see something greater: the former and latter rain together in a greater way in these last seconds of these last hours.

00:04:37.859 --> 00:04:49.999
This is a pillow my wife put on there so you all could see it. I got this at Nancy DeFrain's healing thing she did at the church, and this is Jesus the Healer.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:58.193
What a witness and a testimony of who Jesus is and what He does for the body of Christ to wear.

00:04:58.194 --> 00:05:10.707
You could probably get that on her ministry website, Nancy DeFrain Ministries, but she has these "Jesus the Healer"sweatshirts, and I thought that was so cool, so I got me one.

00:05:10.708 --> 00:05:14.439
But my wife put it on a pillow so you all could see it. It has an eagle on the front, too.

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:20.534
I thought that was pretty cool. I just love the witness of it because it's who I am.

00:05:20.535 --> 00:05:30.624
I believe it with all my heart that Jesus is a healer, and so I said, "That's perfect, I'll wear it."I was excited she got that for me.

00:05:30.625 --> 00:05:41.490
So I just want to encourage you all today about the visitations and the manifestations of angelic encounters.

00:05:41.491 --> 00:06:00.545
I believe what the Lord showed me—He said, "As you're getting closer and closer,"and this was several years ago He told me this—He said, "You're going to start to experience more angelic visitations than you've ever experienced before, Brandon."And it has been so.

00:06:00.546 --> 00:06:07.198
I've had a lot of encounters from angelic help and divine protection.

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:11.604
I've seen secret service angels. The Lord shows me these things, and I'm excited about it.

00:06:11.605 --> 00:06:27.323
But He told me, "I want you to go on and encourage my people today about expecting divine protection, expecting divine whatever."I mean, whatever you need, the Lord has it.

00:06:27.324 --> 00:06:34.332
I believe with all my heart we're in a time like never before. We're going to see things like we've never seen before.

00:06:34.333 --> 00:06:45.595
I'll tell you some of the visitations that I've had on this for just a second—I'll give you one or two of them and then we'll pray—but I just want to encourage you.

00:06:45.596 --> 00:06:52.830
Let's take communion together again. I've got my communion, and I just wanted to lift it up before the Lord.

00:06:52.831 --> 00:07:06.038
Today is Yom Kippur, so it's a day of atonement. I know it's probably already over for some of you, but I'm going to act like it's happening right now.

00:07:06.039 --> 00:07:21.517
Yom Kippur is happening right now, and we're going to take communion just like they did in Washington, D.C., together as believers lifting up America, Australia, Asia, Europe, and Africa.

00:07:21.517 --> 00:07:34.691
We're lifting up our nations before the Lord. If we humble ourselves and pray—He didn't say if the world does this, He said, "If My people do it"—that's us. We're His children.

00:07:34.692 --> 00:07:53.797
He said if you humble yourself and pray and turn from your wicked ways, I believe, Lord, that we turn from our wicked ways and that we'll have one last revival, one last major push, a harvest of souls like we've never seen before.

00:07:53.798 --> 00:08:01.150
I saw great things coming for demonstrations and manifestations: arms growing out, eyes coming back.

00:08:01.151 --> 00:08:07.440
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, walking in the supernatural will be like taking a breath, just like stepping over.

00:08:07.441 --> 00:08:18.854
A lot of times we pray and pray to get over there, but the more you get closer to praying, you'll understand what I'm talking about.

00:08:18.855 --> 00:08:39.796
Praying and interceding sometimes takes time to get over that river, but the Lord said it would be as close as stepping over into those rivers, those geysers, is what I want to call them—to step over and feel that.

00:08:39.797 --> 00:08:44.217
He said it would be like taking a breath; it will be effortless, sweatless victories.

00:08:44.218 --> 00:08:53.500
That's a good word: sweatless victories where you just step into the supernatural and you get your manifestation of what you're believing for like a light switch.

00:08:53.501 --> 00:09:08.463
He said it would be like flipping on a light switch. It's not going to be hard where you intercede for hours to see a turn in the spirit realm; He said it's like taking a breath, you just step over.

00:09:08.464 --> 00:09:16.659
Glory to God! For somebody who prays like I do, that is awesome. It's exciting.

00:09:16.660 --> 00:09:28.612
I just go, "Oh, thank you, Lord."But it's not something far off; I believe it's today as we're entering into this Yom Kippur, the Day of Atonement.

00:09:28.613 --> 00:09:32.416
Rosh Hashanah is over and we've entered into that holy time.

00:09:32.417 --> 00:09:37.654
I believe we're in a time right now—first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:09:37.655 --> 00:10:06.814
I don't want to take your time just jabbering, so let's take this communion today and let's enter into His throne room boldly as His kids, not as orphans or strangers, but friends of the King today.

00:10:06.815 --> 00:10:14.031
I want you all to be bold about it, saying, "Dad, I'm home. I'm here with You.

00:10:14.032 --> 00:10:17.296
I'm sitting on Your throne. I'm seated with You in the heavenlies.

00:10:17.297 --> 00:10:23.945
You dwell in me, and as I breathe, You breathe with me. We're one.

00:10:23.946 --> 00:10:37.420
The Holy Spirit and I are one."So Father, we just lift up this body before You, and we thank You for the Day of Atonement.

00:10:37.421 --> 00:10:47.134
We thank You, Lord, that You've washed us in Your blood, that You have atoned for all our sins.

00:10:47.135 --> 00:11:09.696
You took all our disease, our mental anguish, our suffering, mental torments, depressions, anxieties, and fears.

00:11:09.697 --> 00:11:22.213
Jesus, You paid the price, and it's by Your covenant—by the body that was broken for us. I thank You, Father, that You are our healer.

00:11:22.214 --> 00:11:38.111
According to Your word, Lord, You said, "By My stripes, you are healed."As I take this body, Lord, I thank You that You dwell in me, and there's no place for sickness and disease in my body—no virus.

00:11:38.111 --> 00:11:49.208
We're going into the winter months, Lord, and I thank You that You are my flu shot, You are my C-word shot; You have it all.

00:11:49.209 --> 00:11:58.368
You cover us, and I believe that You are my protector, that no weapon, no pestilence, no plague comes nigh me.

00:11:58.369 --> 00:12:08.523
I take this, Father, and I thank You, Lord; this is my Holy Ghost vaccination. Lord, I thank You for Your protection over me.

00:12:08.524 --> 00:12:23.431
You have been good, and Your mercy is new every morning; Your mercy endures forever.

00:12:23.432 --> 00:12:40.889
Thank You, Father. Now, Lord, we take the blood. We thank You for Your blood, Lord, that all our sins are washed away.

00:12:40.890 --> 00:12:47.117
It is by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:12:47.118 --> 00:12:59.359
It's a holy thing. We don't flippantly do it, but we do it with all our heart.

00:12:59.360 --> 00:13:07.024
Jesus'blood was shed for me, it was shed for them, and I thank You for Your blood.

00:13:07.025 --> 00:13:17.622
I thank You for the cross. I thank You for washing over me. The blood of Jesus washes me, and You watch over me, my children, and my wife.

00:13:17.623 --> 00:13:28.278
Father, I thank You for the protection of Your blood. We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:13:28.279 --> 00:13:46.698
We take this blood right now in the name of Jesus. Thank You, Lord, that You atoned for our sins; You don't even remember them.

00:13:46.699 --> 00:14:00.133
Thank You, Lord, for Your mercy, for healing us by the covenant You gave to us.

00:14:00.134 --> 00:14:17.205
Greater works will we do because You went to the Father and sent us the Comforter, the Holy Spirit, who dwells on the inside of us.

00:14:17.206 --> 00:14:40.621
Holy Spirit, we invite You into this time. Thank You for this day, for this is the day the Lord has made and we will rejoice and be glad in it.

00:14:40.622 --> 00:15:02.832
We want You to be our friend, our standby, our helper. You said You would teach us and guide us into all things. Whatever it is, You have the answer.

00:15:02.833 --> 00:15:23.447
We do not lean on our own intellect—because that would be really bad for me—but Lord, I thank You that we have the mind of Christ.

00:15:23.448 --> 00:15:42.518
I thank You that You're the captain, and I'm not even the co-captain, Lord; I just sit in the back and let You steer the ship in every area of my life.

00:15:42.519 --> 00:15:59.919
Father, I thank You that You have a perfect plan for us—perfect peace, perfect everything—because we're allowing You to steer our lives.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:15.675
You said, "Trust in the Lord with all your heart, and lean not unto your own understanding, but in all your ways acknowledge Him, and He shall direct your paths."We trust You, Lord.

00:16:15.676 --> 00:16:41.789
We let go. It may not make any sense at all, but it doesn't have to when you're trusting Jesus.

00:16:41.790 --> 00:16:47.755
We reach forth and grab onto the new thing, letting go of the past.

00:16:47.756 --> 00:17:09.798
I'm not going to keep looking back over my shoulder; I press on for You, Jesus, and look for the fresh things. God has our future.

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:24.016
"Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health, even as thy soul prospers."So I'm going to talk to you all about angelic visitations.

00:17:24.017 --> 00:17:36.335
One night, my wife and I were lying in bed asleep, probably about 4:00 in the morning, and all of a sudden we felt our whole roof shake.

00:17:36.336 --> 00:17:52.582
I thought somebody was breaking in. It was so strong that it literally felt like something was coming through. It woke us both up.

00:17:52.583 --> 00:18:07.408
I flew out of bed, turned on the light, grabbed my firearm, and was going toward the door when instantaneously my eyes were translated over to the realm of the spirit.

00:18:07.409 --> 00:18:19.613
The Lord allowed me to see these three massive pig-looking demons with long evil noses and eyes that were red and slanted.

00:18:19.614 --> 00:18:35.188
They had scaly skin and long nasty hair—of course, it's a demon.

00:18:35.189 --> 00:18:49.336
One was like a black mist or a fog that you could see through, but it had evil red eyes.

00:18:49.337 --> 00:19:00.577
The other one looked like a pig, and the third one was red and very gnarly-looking with big black horns.

00:19:00.578 --> 00:19:05.168
It looked like something off of A Witch's Invitation with Carman.

00:19:05.169 --> 00:19:17.392
They were hissing and growling, but they couldn't get close to the house. It's like they were being blocked.

00:19:17.393 --> 00:19:29.182
I know I put a bloodline around my home, but at this time I was just staring at them.

00:19:29.183 --> 00:19:37.751
It was like when you see a bull scrape the dirt; they were scraping the dirt like they were trying to get traction to come at me, but they couldn't.

00:19:37.752 --> 00:20:02.026
All of a sudden, I see these massive angelic beings. They were massive, and they had their arms interlocked—they had their hands on their hips and were locked together.

00:20:02.027 --> 00:20:19.562
I believe there were three or four of them. They were standing up, and I bet they were seventeen feet high—massive, bigger than my tree out front—and they were wide.

00:20:19.563 --> 00:20:35.551
They were glowing with glory. When I looked over and saw them protecting me, they didn't have swords or shields; they were just a wall.

00:20:35.552 --> 00:21:02.126
They had these beautiful gowns on, and their voices were like thunder when they spoke. It sounded like a thunderous echo.

00:21:02.127 --> 00:21:36.642
When I saw them standing there, I said, "Praise the Lord!"And when I said that, they turned back and looked at me and said, "Praise the Lord!"They started worshiping the Lord with me.

00:21:36.643 --> 00:21:41.898
Every single time they said "Praise the Lord,"it echoed throughout the neighborhood.

00:21:41.899 --> 00:22:06.833
It wasn't in the natural; it was the spirit. I want to tell you all: the spirit realm is more real than the natural realm.

00:22:06.834 --> 00:22:15.678
It's just one breath away. To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:22:15.679 --> 00:22:58.396
Instantaneously, we go into the spirit realm, and the angels were crying, "Praise the Lord!"At this time, I see a portal open over to the east, and I can see into the glory, into the heavens.

00:22:58.397 --> 00:23:27.692
There was light up there, and you could see the holy city. All of a sudden, when they said "Praise the Lord,"that light from heaven—the glory—shined down on those angels and made them glow.

00:23:27.693 --> 00:23:57.621
They started glowing with the glory, and their faces shined.

00:23:57.622 --> 00:24:20.723
I said, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord!"and they said, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord!"You could hear it through the atmosphere.

00:24:20.724 --> 00:24:37.036
I stood there and watched this for a long time because it was beautiful.

00:24:37.037 --> 00:24:48.775
As I was worshiping, they worshiped with me, and I didn't even pay attention to the devils anymore.

00:24:48.776 --> 00:25:02.675
They went away as we worshiped. I was so fixed on those angelic beings that I had completely forgotten the devils were there.

00:25:02.676 --> 00:25:17.065
When I looked back down, they were gone. I guess they got scared away. But I want to tell you, your angels keep charge over you.

00:25:17.066 --> 00:25:23.682
Psalm 91 says they would bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:25:23.683 --> 00:25:35.999
I believe with all my heart that's happening all the time and we don't even know it.

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:51.542
Well, I went to work the next day at the church. I was so excited because we had a staff meeting.

00:25:51.543 --> 00:25:56.192
I told the pastor the whole thing, and he said, "Brandon, I don't doubt it.

00:25:56.193 --> 00:26:00.842
I actually see a glow on your face."The holy glow was still shining on me.

00:26:00.843 --> 00:26:06.112
He said he could see a tangible manifestation of the spirit of the Lord on my face.

00:26:06.113 --> 00:26:12.002
That visitation changed my life. I learned how to deal with stuff in the spirit realm more and more.

00:26:12.003 --> 00:26:16.342
It's like trial and error—one day at a time. Nobody really ever mentored me.

00:26:16.343 --> 00:26:22.852
I used to think you had to be friends with upper leadership or rub shoulders with them to get your call.

00:26:22.853 --> 00:26:29.362
You go to conferences and want to sit on the front row so they'll notice you and give you a prophecy.

00:26:29.363 --> 00:26:29.462
I realized I went to all the revivals and worked for mega-churches, putting myself in a position to be seen because I knew God had a call on me.

00:26:29.463 --> 00:26:29.562
I wanted any guest speaker or prophet to see me on the front row.

00:26:29.563 --> 00:26:29.662
How many times did I wait in the back room just to say hi to the pastor?

00:26:29.663 --> 00:26:29.862
But the more I pushed for it, the more they looked at me and said, "We don't see it. In fact, we see you're a janitor."And I kept cleaning.

00:26:29.863 --> 00:26:29.962
I had certain dear people who would see it, and big ministers who laid hands on me, but I'd always come back and quote them: "So-and-so said this about me."It gave me just enough encouragement to keep going.

00:26:29.963 --> 00:26:30.162
But you don't need to rub shoulders with your pastor for your call to come to pass. Now I sit in the back row a lot.

00:26:30.163 --> 00:26:30.262
I don't need them to tip their hat toward me; Jesus tipped His hat toward me and said, "Start a YouTube channel."What He's done has been amazing, and nobody else can take the glory for it.

00:26:30.263 --> 00:26:30.562
It was always Jesus. You don't have to have man promote you. He said to me, "Brandon, you cannot earn the anointing; you qualify for it.

00:26:30.563 --> 00:26:30.662
I will equip the qualified."Many in the body try to earn it by giving money or doing things, but there's nothing you can do other than be obedient—walking in His glory and dying to self daily.

00:26:30.663 --> 00:26:30.762
The Apostle Paul said, "I die daily."So I want to encourage you: you don't need a Reinhard Bonnke or somebody to acknowledge the gift on your life.

00:26:30.763 --> 00:26:30.962
Seek Jesus with your whole heart, and He'll bring it to pass. I deliberately sit in the back because I don't need that.

00:26:30.963 --> 00:26:31.062
It was heartbreaking; I went for fifteen years as just the guy in the bathroom.

00:26:31.063 --> 00:26:31.162
I cleaned with all my heart—scrubbing the cracks and the grout—and it wasn't always easy.

00:26:31.163 --> 00:26:31.262
In that process of cleaning up vomit and diarrhea year after year, setting up chairs in the sanctuary, I learned a lot about the mega-church world.

00:26:31.263 --> 00:26:31.362
It's a lot of racket and insecurity, but it's all about Jesus.

00:26:31.363 --> 00:26:31.462
Don't give up on your dream just because somebody doesn't acknowledge you.

00:26:31.463 --> 00:26:31.762
Jesus acknowledges you. Don't despise small beginnings. Volunteering to clean bathrooms—Jesus loves it.

00:26:31.763 --> 00:26:31.862
The greatest visitations I've ever had were behind a commode.

00:26:31.863 --> 00:26:32.062
Seriously, cleaning out feminine trash cans—those are some of the most precious memories I have. He became beautiful in my life during the hard times.

00:26:32.063 --> 00:26:32.162
If you lean not unto your own understanding, the Lord said to put gasoline on their fire, son, and fan them, and He will direct your paths.

00:26:32.163 --> 00:35:53.969
Your boss might treat you like trash, but keep on with the gospel.

00:35:53.970 --> 00:40:41.028
When I get to the other side and He says, "Well done, thy good and faithful servant,"I'll be happy. This side is just a testing ground.

00:40:41.029 --> 00:41:11.322
If you find something lowly to do in the sight of man, you'll reap a great reward during the Thousand-Year Reign.

00:41:11.323 --> 00:41:53.230
The first will be last, and the last will be first. Do everything—whether it's ditch digging or cleaning a stall—all for the glory of God.

00:41:53.231 --> 00:42:19.895
If you're a housewife, do it for the glory of God, and He'll visit you there.

00:42:19.896 --> 00:42:47.236
Many people with a huge spotlight now will be shocked on the other side. Humble yourself under the mighty hand of God.

00:42:47.237 --> 00:43:28.222
When you stand before the judgment seat of Christ, your work will be tested by fire.

00:43:28.223 --> 00:43:46.375
It's either going to burn up as hay and stubble or come out as gold and silver.

00:43:46.376 --> 00:44:30.919
There will be a day when He asks, "What did you do for me?"You'll be accountable for everything.

00:44:30.920 --> 00:44:44.506
Do something with your hands for Him—prayer, volunteering, being a parking lot attendant.

00:44:44.507 --> 00:45:37.648
Do it for His glory, not for man's praise. If you get praise on this side, you aren't getting it over there.

00:45:37.649 --> 00:46:21.463
Look for God to say, "Good job, son."I have to be careful how I say this, but I know a man whose company makes about 50 million dollars a year.

00:46:21.464 --> 00:46:32.267
He gives huge amounts to missions but doesn't want any acknowledgment.

00:46:32.268 --> 00:46:47.947
They wanted to put a plaque on a building he donated, and he didn't want it.

00:46:47.948 --> 00:47:14.882
Everything he touches turns to gold, yet he dresses like an Average Joe.

00:47:14.883 --> 00:47:30.891
I was interceding for him as he gets elderly, and the Lord said, "I want to show you his reward."I saw his robe—the honor he's going to get!

00:47:30.892 --> 00:48:25.449
His robe had beautiful designs like tapestry that represent things he did—badges of honor.

00:48:25.450 --> 00:49:09.367
He is so honored because he gave sacrificially and secretly. He never wanted a monument.

00:49:09.368 --> 00:49:43.472
But on the other side, his badges were gold squares all the way down the hem, with diamonds, emeralds, and sapphires.

00:49:43.473 --> 00:49:58.648
It was gorgeous. So, to God be the glory. I know this is supposed to be a prayer video.

00:49:58.649 --> 00:50:22.266
Father, I thank You for every person here. You said to pray for thirty days, so we lift up this nation in the name of Jesus.

00:50:22.267 --> 00:50:51.439
I thank You for Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur. I thank You that this is a time of celebration and harvest.

00:50:51.440 --> 00:51:08.703
I call the eyes of their understanding to be enlightened, and we take authority over the blinders. We plead the blood of Jesus over their eyes.

00:51:08.704 --> 00:51:24.260
